    <h1>RE&#xAD;TAIN SIN&#xAD;GA&#xAD;POREAN WORK&#xAD;ERS</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200901/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-09-01"><time>2020-09-01</time></a>
        - <span>FRONT PAGE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>In cir­cum­stances where re­trench­ment is un­avoid­able, and an em­ployer has to choose be­tween a for­eigner and Sin­ga­porean, I urge the em­ployer to lean to­wards keep­ing the Sin­ga­porean. In short, if em­ploy­ers must re­trench, re­tain the Sin­ga­porean over for­eigner.</p>
    <p>’’ MS GAN SIOW HUANG, Min­is­ter of State for Man­power and Ed­u­ca­tion.</p>

